data.text:
Joel Thomas Zimmerman, known under deadmau5, is a Canadian progressive house music producer. He is friends with Zedd.

Friendship[]

Zedd supported deadmau5 during select shows on his Meowingtons Hax Tour.

On May 16, 2012, Zedd posted a collage of eight images making puns of his own stage name. One of the names was "Zedd Mau5", a wordplay on "deadmau5".[1]

On October 13, 2012, deadmau5 gave Zedd a tattoo.[2]

Deadmau5 interviewed Zedd in 2013 as part of a YouTube video series.
